tt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马耳他马特。图片来源：Vinca Petersen" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Matt-Maltese">马特·马耳他（Matt Maltese）</a>从即将发行的专辑“她的她”中分享了他渴望的新单曲《我的一生》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/matt-maltese-interview-in-conversation-good-morning-its-now-tomorrow-3048883">我们从与Matt Maltese的对话视频聊天中学到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>柔和，深情和浪漫的曲目使马耳他人承认他对伴侣的爱以及他向他们渴望了多少。 <em>“我摔倒在你的手中 /改变了世界 /挑战，意在想让你更多，”</em>他用平滑的低音线和美丽的钢琴布置唱歌。</p><p>在新闻稿中，马耳他分享了这首歌：“我在一首歌中做了最多的渴望。 </p><p><iframe title="为你一生" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jl9_6Q8cml0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我的一生”为您提供了马耳他即将发行的第六张专辑“ Hers”的第三个品尝者，该专辑定于5月16日通过The Orchard发行（<a href="https://mattmaltese.orcd.co/hers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>预订/预先保存）。该曲目遵循先前发布的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/matt-maltese-returns-with-wistful-single-anytime-anyplace-anyhow-listen-3831032">随时随地，任何地方，无论如何</a>”和“始终有MF”。</p><p> “她的”是马耳他第二张LP“ Krystal”以来的第一张完全自我制作的专辑。新闻稿分享了这张专辑是他的“迄今为止最孤立，最亲密的”和“在暮光之城中存在，将衷心的歌曲创作和干燥的巫术与柔和的弦乐搭配，木管乐器的蓬勃发展或吱吱作响的旧钢琴的声音。”</p><p>在谈到这张专辑时，马耳他分享了很多音乐，这些音乐来自一个痴迷的地方，但是这张唱片是关于长期爱情的反思。</p><p>他继续说：“我足以让自己写这么多情歌的耻辱。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847310" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847310" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847310" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="马特·马耳他的“她的”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847310" class="wp-caption-text">马特·马耳他的“她的”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>“她的”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1。&#39;Arthouse Cinema&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“公共汽车更换火车”</strong><br /> <strong>3。&#39;生日快乐&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4。&#39;随时随地，无论如何&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5。&#39;总是一些MF&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>6。“为空虚治愈”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“从你自己那里度假”</strong><br /> <strong>8。</strong><br /> <strong>9。“一尘不染的永恒黑暗”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“纠结”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“每个人都像我一样疯狂&#39;</strong></p><p>音乐家还宣布了在美国，欧洲和英国进行的标题巡回演出。您可以查看以下日期的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=htt